data.title: Convert German Marks (DEM) and Japanese Yen (JPY): Currency Exchange Rate Conversion Calculator
data.meta_description: Calculator to convert money in German Mark (DEM) to and from Japanese Yen (JPY) using up to date exchange rates.
data.text:
This German Mark and Japanese Yen convertor is up to date with exchange rates from May 26, 2024.

Enter the amount to be converted in the box to the left of German Mark. Use "Swap currencies" to make Japanese Yen the default currency. Click on Japanese Yen or German Marks to convert between that currency and all other currencies.

The German Mark is the currency in Germany (DE, DEU). The Japanese Yen is the currency in Japan (JP, JPN, JAP). The German Mark is also known as Deutschmark, and Deutsche Mark. The Japanese Yen is divided into 100 sen. The exchange rate for the German Mark was last updated on May 23, 2024 from The International Monetary Fund. The exchange rate for the Japanese Yen was last updated on May 23, 2024 from The International Monetary Fund. The DEM conversion factor has 6 significant digits. The JPY conversion factor has 6 significant digits.
